headline: 6 of the best stocks from Trump's first 100 days — and 3 of the worst
summary: The first 100 days of the Trump administration unleashed economic chaos throughout the U.S. economy, including the stock market, which saw the worst first 100 days of a presidency since Nixon. Still, there were winners (and losers) among the S&P 500.

headline: Deckers vs. Nike: Which Shoe Stock Is the Better Buy Right Now?
summary: Shares of Nike and Deckers are down big this year as tariffs and concerns about the economy are weighing on their prospects.  Nike is significantly larger, but it's in the midst of a turnaround and faces several question marks.  Nike (NYSE: NKE) and Deckers Outdoor (NYSE: DECK) are two stocks that have been struggling this year.
